Class Algorithm

  java.lang.Thread
      jml.basics.Algorithm

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class Algorithm
extends java.lang.Thread

Title: Algorithm

Description: This class is an abstract version of an algorithm.

A subclass that implements the Algorithm class can receive the algorithm inputs in the constructor.

tracer

public java.util.Vector tracer
Indicates the trace level of an algorithm. Useful for keeping information of the algorithm execution. A level >= 0 indicates that the algorithm will store its intermediate results. A level lower than 0 indicates that the algorithm will just keep the output
